<h1>ISPyB for industrials or laboratory outside <%=Constants.SITE_NAME%></h1>
<h2>You can log in ISPyB with your NICE login and password.</h2>
<br>
Outside of <%=Constants.SITE_NAME%>, ISPyB will provide you with an interface : 
<ul>
<li>to retrieve and fulfill information about your proteins samples coming from samplesheets</li>
<li>to enter information about the dewars you are planning to send,</li>
<li>to enter information about the samples which are stored in these dewars,</li>
<li>to view reports about your collected data</li>
</ul>
